Mero
====

Build
-----

    $ ./autogen.sh
    $ ./configure
    $ make

or in one command:

    $ ./scripts/m0 rebuild


Test
----

    $ ./scripts/m0 run-all


Get to know
-----------

    doc/source-structure
    doc/coding-style
    doc/todo

Go deep...

Still surfing? Surf this:

    doc/reading-list.html

    $ make doc
    $ x-www-browser doc/html/index.html

Welcome, Earthling!
